gitCommit.subject: Fix linting errors and add BDD/E2E tests to CI/CD pipeline
gitCommit.body:
Fix linting errors and add BDD/E2E tests to CI/CD pipeline

- Fixed all golangci-lint errcheck and staticcheck issues
- Added logger parameter to DatabaseService constructor
- Created MockLogger for BDD tests
- Updated CI workflow with dedicated jobs for BDD and E2E tests
- Updated release workflow to run all tests before creating releases
- Enhanced error handling in database operations and JSON encoding

Co-authored-by: intel352 <77607+intel352@users.noreply.github.com>
